# Naming Conventions

## Variable Prefixes

| Prefix | Type | Example |
|--------|------|---------|
| `b` | BOOL | `bEnable`, `bError`, `bDone` |
| `n` | INT, DINT, UINT, UDINT, ... | `nCount`, `nState`, `nIndex` |
| `f` | REAL, LREAL | `fPower`, `fCurrent_A`, `fTemperature` |
| `s` | STRING | `sName`, `sTopic`, `sPayload` |
| `t` | TIME | `tTimeout`, `tDelay`, `tCycleTime` |
| `e` | ENUM | `eState`, `eMode`, `eError` |
| `st` | STRUCT instance | `stParam`, `stConfig`, `stMeasurement` |
| `fb` | FB instance | `fbTimer`, `fbPidControl`, `fbJson` |
| `arr` | ARRAY | `arrValues`, `arrCurrent` |
| `hr` | HRESULT | `hrErrorCode` |
| `p` | POINTER | `pPayload`, `pBuffer` |
| `i` | INTERFACE | `iWidget`, `iBase` |
| `c` | Constant (VAR CONSTANT) | `cMaxRetries`, `cTimeout` |
| `cf` | Constant REAL (inline) | `cfNoDataValue`, `cfMinPower` |

## Scope Prefixes

| Prefix | Scope | Example |
|--------|-------|---------|
| `_` | Private/internal VAR (combined with type) | `_nStep`, `_bInitialized`, `_fbTonTest` |
| *(none)* | VAR_INPUT / VAR_OUTPUT | `bEnable`, `fPower`, `stParam` |

## FB Instances — Specific Patterns

| Pattern | Naming | Example |
|---------|--------|---------|
| R_TRIG | `_posEdge{Purpose}` | `_posEdgePlugged`, `_posEdgeReset` |
| F_TRIG | `_negEdge{Purpose}` | `_negEdgePlugged`, `_negEdgeDone` |
| TON | `_fbTon{Purpose}` | `_fbTonTest`, `_fbTonFailsafe` |
| TOF | `_fbTof{Purpose}` | `_fbTofDelay` |

## Type Names

| Kind | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Function Block | `FB_[Lib]_[Purpose]` | `FB_EMS_ECabinet`, `FB_EMS_PID` |
| Internal FB | `FB_[Lib]_[Purpose]` (in `[internal]` folder) | `FB_EMS_FloatingAvg_1m` |
| Function | `F_[Lib]_[Purpose]` | `F_EMS_ReduceInstancePath` |
| Struct | `ST_[Lib]_[Purpose]` | `ST_EMS_ECabinet_Param` |
| Enum | `E_[Lib]_[Purpose]` | `E_EMS_ReleaseMode` |
| String alias | `T_[Purpose]` | `T_MaxString` |
| GVL Params | `Param_[Lib]` | `Param_EMS` |
| GVL Globals | `GVL_[Domain]` | `GVL_EMS` |
| GVL Version | `Global_Version` | — |

## Actions & Methods

| Kind | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Action | `A_[Verb][Object]` | `A_CalculateGridCurrent`, `A_HandleFailsafe` |
| Method | `M_[Verb][Object]` or `[Verb][Object]` | `M_Init`, `SetParam` |
| Property | `[Noun]` (PascalCase) | `IsValid`, `MaxCurrent` |

## Files

- FBs/Functions: `[TypeName].TcPOU` — `FB_EMS_ECabinet.TcPOU`
- DUTs: `[TypeName].TcDUT` — `ST_EMS_ECabinet_Param.TcDUT`, `E_EMS_Mode.TcDUT`
- GVLs: `[GVLName].TcGVL` — `Param_EMS.TcGVL`
- XML `Name` attribute **must** match the type name in the CDATA declaration

## Units in Names

Append unit suffix to physical values: `fCurrent_A`, `fPower_W`, `fEnergy_kWh`, `tDelay_ms`.
In structs, group by purpose, not by type.
